<item>
            <title>[SPR-2789] UrlFilenameViewController backward compatibility broken</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2789</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In version 1.2.8 UrlFilenameViewController maps the url &quot;/products/view.html&quot; to &quot;view&quot; while version 2.0 maps the same url to &quot;products/view&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="15392">SPR-2789</key>
            <summary>UrlFilenameViewController backward compatibility broken</summary>
